2004-08-25	Ole Reinhardt   <ole.reinhardt@kernelconcepts.de>
	* network.c: Support for Wireless LAN devices, automatically WiFi detection,
	             improved automaticaly device detection (add device command)
	* cfgfile.*: Support for Wireless LAN devices. Writes and reads the following
		     parameters in /etc/network/interfaces:
		     
		     - wireless_essid 
		     - wireless_mode
		     - wireless_channel
		     - wireless_key

